<h1>Products Index</h1>

<p>Note: this is the back end, solely for use of site admins.  It is their job to input the company's prices, add in companies, insert more products into the table.  The table is fully sortable and editable, try using the arrow keys, tab, and enter to navigate. </p>


<br><br>

<button type="button" class="saveProducts">Save Changes</button> <br>
<br>

<form>
	<% if(typeof categoriesArray !== "undefined"){ %>
		<% for(i = 0; i < categoriesArray.length; i++) { %>
		<label>
			<input type="checkbox" name="categoryList" value="<%= categoriesArray[i] %>" class="categoryFilter" checked/>
			<%= categoriesArray[i] %>
		</label>
		<% }; %>
	<% }; %>
</form>

<div id="productsTable"></div>

<h2>Add a Product</h2>
<form class="productAdd">
	<label>Category:
		<input type="text" name="category">
	</label>
	<label>Product:
		<input type="text" name="name">
	</label>
	<label>Manufacturer:
		<input type="text" name="manufacturer">
	</label>	
	<input type="submit" value="Add Product">
</form>

